  <li><a href="https://thecomeonman.github.io/xPo">A post explaining how it works</a> with some EPL teams and players analysed</li>
  <li><a href="https://thecomeonman.github.io/xPoDashboard">A dashboard which you could use to analyse a team</a> built on data from Barcelona’s 2008-09 season data from Statsbomb</li>
